<Layout title="About">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">More about me</h1>
  <p>
    I'm a 23 year old software engineer at Thomson Reuters working on their
    Westlaw Precision product. I mostly focus on the backend involving the
    Spring Java Framework, Tomcat, and REST APIs. I care about writing
    maintainable code, understanding the tools I use, and documenting
    everything. I deeply value
    <span class="font-bold"
      >sharing knowledge, educating others, and understanding new viewpoints</span
    > whether that be in computer science topics, my personal and professional life,
    or ways of life.
  </p>

